By completing the AWS101 Architecture workshop, I designed and implemented a secure, internet-connected AWS cloud infrastructure from scratch.

I worked with:

* AWS VPC Design
* Subnetting & Routing
* Internet Gateway Configuration
* EC2 Deployment
* Security Group Management
* Elastic IP Association
* Amazon S3
* IAM Roles & Policies
* Cloud Networking Fundamentals

This project demonstrates practical experience in designing a secure AWS network, deploying compute resources, integrating storage, and implementing identity-based access control following best practices.

